<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 00:32:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>降雨迫使加沙人离开临时营地，增加了疾病风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/rain-forces-gazans-out-of-makeshift-camps-increases-risk-of-disease/0000018c-650e-d798-adac-e5afa6bc0000</link><description>加沙南部流离失所的巴勒斯坦人营地的洪水加剧了本已严重的人道主义危机，影响了数万家庭。更令人担忧的是近东救济工程处和其他援助组织显然无力提供援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/rain-forces-gazans-out-of-makeshift-camps-increases-risk-of-disease/0000018c-650e-d798-adac-e5afa6bc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁阻止摩萨德主席在卡塔尔重启人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-blocks-mossad-chief-from-restarting-hostage-talks-in-qatar/0000018c-64ee-dbd5-a39c-ffffefd60000</link><description>以色列战时内阁决定不提出新协议框架，怀疑卡塔尔谈判是否有效</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 21:18:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-blocks-mossad-chief-from-restarting-hostage-talks-in-qatar/0000018c-64ee-dbd5-a39c-ffffefd60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定，改革派和保守派皈依者有资格获得包皮环切补贴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/reform-conservative-converts-qualify-for-subsidized-circumcisions-top-israeli-court-says/0000018c-63c3-d798-adac-e7ef22640000</link><description>经过十多年的努力，高等法院本周决定，在拉比批准的州皈依计划之外的皈依者也必须获得国家对程序的援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:25:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/reform-conservative-converts-qualify-for-subsidized-circumcisions-top-israeli-court-says/0000018c-63c3-d798-adac-e7ef22640000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装在以色列经济战中开辟了新的危险战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthis-open-new-and-dangerous-front-in-israels-economic-war/0000018c-63a6-dbd5-a39c-fff75c430000</link><description>对与以色列有联系的船只的袭击威胁到以色列进出口的主要路线。对以色列来说幸运的是，红海的全球贸易也面临风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthis-open-new-and-dangerous-front-in-israels-economic-war/0000018c-63a6-dbd5-a39c-fff75c430000</guid></item><item><title>美国并未经历反以色列浪潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/america-is-not-experiencing-an-anti-israel-tidal-wave/0000018c-6333-d6f9-afbc-7f7b36770000</link><description>以色列人痴迷于美国对加沙哈马斯战争的反应，许多人认为，由于这场冲突，美国人正在背叛他们的老盟友。对最近调查的分析表明情况更加复杂</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 17:44:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/america-is-not-experiencing-an-anti-israel-tidal-wave/0000018c-6333-d6f9-afbc-7f7b36770000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人看不到来自加沙的图像，因为我们的记者没有尽职尽责”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-13/ty-article-podcast/israelis-dont-see-images-from-gaza-because-our-journalists-are-not-doing-their-job/0000018c-5e34-de43-affd-fe36d3a70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 16:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-13/ty-article-podcast/israelis-dont-see-images-from-gaza-because-our-journalists-are-not-doing-their-job/0000018c-5e34-de43-affd-fe36d3a70000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装威胁红海船只，西方陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-houthis-exercise-leverage-by-threatening-intl-maritime-security-the-west-stumbles/0000018c-6396-dbd5-a39c-fff78d0d0000</link><description>也门胡塞政权有能力瘫痪曼德海峡世界上最重要的航道，对美国和该地区国家构成难以容忍的威胁</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 15:50:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-houthis-exercise-leverage-by-threatening-intl-maritime-security-the-west-stumbles/0000018c-6396-dbd5-a39c-fff78d0d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列对其公民使用有争议的程序，我们现在就需要讨论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-used-a-procedure-against-its-citizens-we-need-to-talk-about-it-now/0000018c-6383-de43-affd-f783212e0000</link><description>10月7日贝埃里劫持人质事件中，以色列是否执行了所谓的汉尼拔指令——该指令允许军队危及士兵以防止他们被绑架？</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 15:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-israel-used-a-procedure-against-its-citizens-we-need-to-talk-about-it-now/0000018c-6383-de43-affd-f783212e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属在以色列国防军加沙地面行动期间在耶路撒冷集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-rally-in-jerusalem-amid-idf-ground-operation-in-gaza/0000018c-6382-de43-affd-f7820de30000</link><description>在加沙被哈马斯扣押的人质的家人在哈马斯隧道中竖立了一个模拟被囚禁的装置，他们认为释放剩余人质不再是公众议程上的重要议题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 15:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-rally-in-jerusalem-amid-idf-ground-operation-in-gaza/0000018c-6382-de43-affd-f7820de30000</guid></item><item><title>他智胜了哈马斯恐怖分子，但不会回到他的基布兹：“住在坟墓里让我害怕”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-outwitted-hamas-terrorists-but-wont-go-back-it-scares-me-to-live-in-a-tomb/0000018c-5e68-d6f9-afbc-5f6a467d0000</link><description>埃兰·斯米兰斯基从未练习过在真正的袭击中该怎么做，所以他不得不在10月7日临时凑合。他拿着一支步枪和几颗子弹，与哈马斯恐怖分子玩了几个小时的猫捉老鼠游戏，救出了受伤的邻居。一个关于生存和智谋的故事</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 14:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/he-outwitted-hamas-terrorists-but-wont-go-back-it-scares-me-to-live-in-a-tomb/0000018c-5e68-d6f9-afbc-5f6a467d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡尽管呼吁在战争中避免政治，但仍在与利库德集团的亲信进行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-engages-in-political-consultations-despite-own-calls-to-avoid-it-amid-war/0000018c-62c1-d6f9-afbc-7fcb16f50000</link><description>最近与总理关系密切的立法者和顾问举行了磋商，讨论了内塔尼亚胡有关《奥斯陆协议》的信息以及确保本尼·甘茨所在政党的吉迪恩·萨尔部长继续担任内阁成员的方法</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:27:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-engages-in-political-consultations-despite-own-calls-to-avoid-it-amid-war/0000018c-62c1-d6f9-afbc-7fcb16f50000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日的大屠杀让这位伊拉克犹太作家回想起可怕的回忆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-massacre-brings-back-horrific-memories-for-this-iraqi-jewish-author/0000018c-62c5-dbd5-a39c-fff7971b0000</link><description>1969 年 1 月，九名犹太人因间谍罪被判在巴格达被绞死。几分钟路程外，15 岁的莫娜·叶海亚 (Mona Yahia) 因为害怕人群而躲在家里。这些景象仍然新鲜，并在她的新半自传小说中被精美地捕捉到</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 12:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-massacre-brings-back-horrific-memories-for-this-iraqi-jewish-author/0000018c-62c5-dbd5-a39c-fff7971b0000</guid></item><item><title>在罕见批评后，拜登派遣高级顾问前往以色列就加沙战争时间表进行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/after-rare-critique-of-israel-biden-dispatches-top-adviser-for-talks-on-gaza-timetable/0000018c-628f-d6f9-afbc-7fcf2a910000</link><description>以色列官员担心，美国国家安全顾问抵达以色列后，美国将在几周内结束加沙战争的最后期限。其他来访的美国高级官员也有这样的印象：内塔尼亚胡寻求在加沙“后天”与拜登公开对抗</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 11:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/after-rare-critique-of-israel-biden-dispatches-top-adviser-for-talks-on-gaza-timetable/0000018c-628f-d6f9-afbc-7fcf2a910000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，尽管初步就条款进行了谈判，但以色列与哈马斯续签人质协议仍遥遥无期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/renewed-israeli-hamas-hostage-deal-distant-despite-initial-talks-for-terms-sources-say/0000018c-6253-dbd5-a39c-ff73a5360000</link><description>一名以色列官员估计，哈马斯可能会试图推动一项新的协议，以进一步缓解以色列国防军战斗中的挫折。虽然哈马斯的目标是推进一项“所有人为所有人”的协议，但据报道，以色列更愿意寻求一项植根于人道主义原则的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 09:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/renewed-israeli-hamas-hostage-deal-distant-despite-initial-talks-for-terms-sources-say/0000018c-6253-dbd5-a39c-ff73a5360000</guid></item><item><title>加沙地带北部9名以色列士兵丧生的战斗背后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-including-idf-brigade-commander-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-617b-d798-adac-e5ff9ac80000</link><description>在舒贾耶耶被杀的士兵是恐怖武装分子向在该地区活动的以色列国防军开火时发起的协同伏击的受害者。一旦担心他们可能被绑架到附近的隧道，另一支部队赶来解救士兵，却遭遇了类似的伏击</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 07:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-including-idf-brigade-commander-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-617b-d798-adac-e5ff9ac80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对哈马斯的军事优势在加沙北部拥挤的城市地区被削弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-edge-over-hamas-is-blunted-in-crowded-areas-of-northern-gaza/0000018c-5fe4-dbd5-a39c-fff7003f0000</link><description>以色列国防军仍未控制 Shujaiyeh，但在 Jabalya 难民营遇到的阻力有所减少 ■ 尽管人质处境悲惨，但以色列政府似乎并不急于达成另一项协议 ■ 没有迹象表明哈马斯认为其谈判地位已经恶化</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 04:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-edge-over-hamas-is-blunted-in-crowded-areas-of-northern-gaza/0000018c-5fe4-dbd5-a39c-fff7003f0000</guid></item><item><title>被认为被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列人被谋杀；内塔尼亚胡：任何国际压力都无法阻止战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-live/report-israel-flooding-hamas-tunnels-idf-retrieves-bodies-of-two-hostages-from-gaza/0000018c-6126-d798-adac-e5af76d80000</link><description>周二，九名以色列国防军士兵在加沙地带北部的舒贾耶地区遭到伏击身亡，其中一人在附近的另一起事件中丧生 ■ 据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列开始向哈马斯隧道注入海水 ■ 从加沙遣返的两名以色列人质的尸体 ■拜登：内塔尼亚胡“必须改变他的政府”，以色列因加沙狂轰滥炸而失去支持 ■ 以色列国防军更新战争中受伤士兵人数至 1,645 名 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 03:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-live/report-israel-flooding-hamas-tunnels-idf-retrieves-bodies-of-two-hostages-from-gaza/0000018c-6126-d798-adac-e5af76d80000</guid></item><item><title>罗格斯大学加入了越来越多打压亲巴勒斯坦学生团体的大学行列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/rutgers-joins-growing-list-of-universities-clamping-down-on-pro-palestinian-student-group/0000018c-6031-dbd5-a39c-ff7371350000</link><description>巴勒斯坦正义学生会周一接到通知，其罗格斯-新不伦瑞克分会已被暂停，因为收到多起投诉，称其扰乱了课堂、项目、膳食和学生学习</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 02:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/rutgers-joins-growing-list-of-universities-clamping-down-on-pro-palestinian-student-group/0000018c-6031-dbd5-a39c-ff7371350000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的疾病蔓延危及哈马斯扣押的人质，很快甚至会危及以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/morbidity-in-gaza-endangers-the-hostages-and-possibly-israel/0000018c-5fe1-d6f9-afbc-5febf3e60000</link><description>加沙人面临着多种疾病的风险，这些疾病不能仅限于政治边界。 “我估计几周之内我们就会开始在以色列感受到这一点。本-古里安大学公共卫生学院的一位高级健康学者表示，最初，它将在南部地区传播，然后由士兵传播。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 01:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/morbidity-in-gaza-endangers-the-hostages-and-possibly-israel/0000018c-5fe1-d6f9-afbc-5febf3e60000</guid></item><item><title>专家警告以色列政府法案提议总理允许辛贝特秘密搜查手机和电脑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/experts-amendment-to-surveillance-law-would-give-israeli-pm-great-power-without-oversight/0000018c-5fc7-de43-affd-ffc7136f0000</link><description>专家：监视法修正案将赋予以色列总理不受监督的巨大权力。以色列政府希望让 Shin Bet 使用间谍软件秘密搜索手机和计算机，并访问包含其“完成工作所需”信息的数据库</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 00:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/experts-amendment-to-surveillance-law-would-give-israeli-pm-great-power-without-oversight/0000018c-5fc7-de43-affd-ffc7136f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>